message.content: Gay, a little puzzled, went through to the bar. Doc and Silygom were sitting just inside having coffee. "Come and join us and bring your boy friend," Doc called. "No, Doc!" Silygom remonstrated. "They want to be alone." "I've booked a table at the cafe"," Doc said, "they are packed tonight so come and join us if you can't find a table for two."
